# Overall Story (WIP)

Year: 27BC

You are a pack of Orcs that follow the guidance of the #HollowKing.
You have been in a centuries long war with the Humans (Every Other Humanoid Creature).
The war started because the Humans got greedy for land and started invading Orc camps, driving them out of their homes, just so the humans can colonize the land and use it for themselves.

You are a team of highly trained warriors from the #BloodmoonWarband Pack that have been tasked with completing the ritual and raising the Hollow King back from the dead.

Centuries ago, in the Year 2000BC, The Hollow King Ruled over the whole land with the Orcs under him, then Humans arrived from the West and at first were friendly and helped the Orcs thrive, then the humans got greedy and started taking land, slaughtering Orc kind and driving them away from their homes. Then the Great War broke out with the Hollow King leading the way. Orc victory was upon them, but one Battle the Hollow King was killed leading his army forward, his death lead to the downfall of the Orcs and the Humans quickly reclaimed lost ground and ever expanding their empire.

During this story you the PCs will take on the Humans, doing quests for friendly factions, and advance your way towards the Hollow Kings Tomb to bring him back and have him again lead the battle against the Humans and reclaim the land your kind once called home.


